<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落到一辆卡车上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>僵尸们跌跌撞撞地从乐购超市出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的嘴上沾满了面包渣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到一个僵尸身上粘着勒·斯威特面包厂的包装纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个僵尸不是演《大力士》的演员吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们边跑边叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！僵尸！”一个老人大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个十几岁的少年开始逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中一个拿着手机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要自拍……啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”大力士僵尸咯吱咯吱嚼着手机，然后吐了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿跑去追朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到几个人躲在出租车上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，救救我们！”僵尸们伸出手抓人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个老人对着僵尸们挥着他的拐杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“离我们远一点，你们这些怪物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西飞快地飞上天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用超级呼吸吹气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些僵尸摔倒后滚到了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑！”罗西对人们说，“找个地方躲起来。我很快就回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到勒·斯威特面包厂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面，有两个巨大的烤箱在墙的一侧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器发出很大的响声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>装满甜甜圈的传送带慢慢地滚动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一台机器在甜甜圈上加糖霜，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一台机器把甜甜圈运到巧克力浆中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得把这些机器关上。它在生产甜甜圈，还有僵尸！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把所有机器都关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包厂变得很安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，罗西听到了脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个戴着围裙和高高的白帽子的男人跑了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？”他大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他看到了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，先生！”罗西说，“你也许不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的甜甜圈引起了很大麻烦。你知道……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以为你可以阻止我吗？”那个男人生气地看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”罗西很困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人接着说：“ 我叫皮特·勒·斯威特，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我发明了一种特殊的甜甜圈配方。它太好吃了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的人都只想要吃它——我的甜甜圈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大笑。“你阻止不了我，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西眯起了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是有意把人变成僵尸的？而不是一个意外？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特扬起了一边的眉毛。“什么？僵尸？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西两手掐腰。“你的特殊配方糟透了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的甜甜圈把人变成了僵尸！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要我能多卖甜甜圈，管他呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手放在拉杆上。“再见了，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勒·斯威特拉了一下拉杆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巧克力酱洒出来，把罗西完全盖住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>